Class AbstractMatch<A extends Bigraph<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.AbstractMatch<A>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - the kind of bigraph the match belongs.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Match<A>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Match

    public abstract class AbstractMatch<A extends Bigraph<?>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Match<A>
    This class provides some support for implementing the interface . The support is limited to handling context, redex and parameter composing a match; but no sanity checks are performed on these, nor on their interfaces.
